      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Things seem to be coming nicely\nthese days for the local union Of\nelectrical workers. Recently a\nscale was signed by the Traction\ncompany and today the local con-\ntractors signed a scale, which\ngives the men substantial in\ncrease in wages and other conces-\nsions. The present scale for jour\nney men is $3.50 per day and the\nnew scale is 81. First class help\ners will receive hereafter So per\nday.\n\n\nThe contractors also agree to\nthe closed shop and will not ask\ntheir employers to work on any\nbuilding declared unfair by the\nStructural alliance. The new scale\ntakes effect September /."
    }
  ]
